{"tid":1665980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無論裝修幾多商鋪，都只係一個「聲明」","createTime":"2019-10-20T18:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T11:24:31.000Z","uid":129622,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f0375cd9dbe4507355b0246a59bde9605002c6b3","tid":1665980,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T18:47:43.000Z","msg":"我地藉此向世界宣揚拒絕紅資<br />\n但想用來斷絕中共水喉就唔太有效<br />\n更遑論威脅中共權力<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但我地知道政府既四肢在於各部門 城市既命脈在於鐵路<br />\n</span></strong>點解做咁多手腳係黨鐵？<br />\n因為黨鐵可以停半日 但唔可以停足一星期<br />\n短暫停站可以處理示威或者恐慌 <br />\n但長期短鐵城市就會跟住停頓<br />\n<br />\n然後係政府部門<br />\n之前話稅局會搞到好多人 又話大廈危險<br />\n同樣都會影響到市民<br />\n裝修商鋪係拖症 一次過令政府停擺 斷臂救命先係解決方法<br />\n另外裝修何嘗唔係面對危險？<br />\n但起碼目標集中 更加係對准政權<br />\n<br />\n戰線開太多 目標分得太散 唔單止國際 連香港人都開始迷失<br />\n真係好希望71立法會果種齊心同明確會再次出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n訓 跑左成日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab956ae3ea943193dbe65b3315efa5ad215979f","tid":1665980,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T18:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0354b23dac799c93bad2788f2f720d3492c26208","tid":1665980,"uid":322304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T18:55:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4e9c1889a21cedbec55ae465f9052559d662971","tid":1665980,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55807aefc11a12d0992cb38d44e45372a1659b8a","tid":1665980,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b99e4afc3aed510ed006419267c1d772cacca6","tid":1665980,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}